title: Ep. - 340 - SHEP ROSE FROM SOUTHERN CHARM REVIEW OF ON POINTE ON DISNEY PLUS
description:
Shep Rose is a cast member on Bravo’s Southern Charm and the author of the new book Average Expectations: Lessons in Lowering the Bar. He talks about wild stories from traveling, becoming a tv personality, and his favorite movies and books.

 

Choreographer Liana-Marie Alvarez reviews On Pointe on Disney Plus, a six-part docuseries that follows students and captures a season in the School of American Ballet (SAB) in New York City.
